import React, { useState, useParams, useEffect } from 'react' import axios from 'axios' function Read() { const [data, setData] = useState([]) const { id } = useParams() useEffect(() => { axios.get(`/student/${id}`) .then((res) => { console.log(res.data) setData(res.data) }) .catch((err) => console.log(err)) }, [id]) return (
Name E-mail Age Gender
{data[0].name} {data[0].email} {data[0].age} {data[0].gender}
) } export default Read
